sequenceDiagram
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant MCP as pry-mcp
    participant OS as macOS
    participant APP as Target app (PryHarness)

    CC->>MCP: pry_run_spec(path)
    MCP->>MCP: parse spec
    MCP->>OS: NSWorkspace.open(bundle)
    OS->>APP: launch
    APP->>APP: PryHarness.start() binds socket
    MCP->>APP: connect /tmp/pry-<bundle>.sock
    APP-->>MCP: hello OK

    loop for each step
        MCP->>OS: AX query (resolve target)
        OS-->>MCP: frame / role / label
        MCP->>OS: CGEventPost(click)
        OS->>APP: deliver event
        MCP->>APP: read_state / read_logs
        APP-->>MCP: snapshot
    end

    MCP->>MCP: format verdict.md
    MCP-->>CC: verdict (markdown + path)
